---
layout: default
pagination:
  data: collections
  size: 1
  alias: tag
  filter:
    - all
    - posts
    - snippets
    - recipes
    - postStats
permalink: /tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/
eleventyComputed:
  description: All the posts that are tagged with “{{ tag }}”.
  title: "{{ tag }}"
---

{% render "styles.liquid",
  inline: site.configuration.inline_styles,
  partials: "
    components/list,
    components/tags
  "
%}

{% assign items = collections[ tag ] | reverse %}
{% assign count = items | size %}

{% markdown %}
This page lists {% if count == 1 %}the *one* entry{% else %}all <strong>{{ count }}</strong> entries{% endif %} tagged with the word “{{ tag }}”.
I hope you find what you’re looking for. 🚀 If looking for something specific, try the [search](/blog/search/).
{% endmarkdown %}

{% render "post_list.liquid", items: items %}
